Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.30,0:00:07.18,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I still can't believe you're letting me stay here…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.18,0:00:08.34,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,as your pupil…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.34,0:00:10.05,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Shining armor is a father!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:11.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm an aunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.52,0:00:14.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You first friendship lesson is going to be…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.03,0:00:16.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,reuniting with Sunburst!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:17.98,Sunburst,,0,0,0,, Yes. That's me. Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:18.87,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Important wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:21.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The baby is an alicorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.15,0:00:22.99,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,So she can be a superstrong flyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.99,0:00:24.99,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And have crazy baby magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:31.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,, Without the Heart, the Crystal Empire is about to be buried under a mountain of ice and snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:13.18,Rarity,,0,0,0,,So…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.18,0:01:17.34,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Not only can we not take party on the fabilous ancient ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:20.25,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But're also about to be frozen solid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:22.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Without the Crystal Heart's magical protection
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.92,0:01:25.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,the entire city is about to become a winter wasteland.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:30.31,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But… What about when king Sombra ruled the Crystal Empire only Crystal Heart was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.31,0:01:32.19,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,The city wasn't covered in snow then!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:33.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The Heart wasn't missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.83,0:01:35.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It was still in the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:37.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,King Sombra had just hidden it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.30,0:01:39.38,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid Twilight is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.38,0:01:41.74,Celestia,,0,0,0,,And the storm clouds are already forming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:46.23,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I can totally fly up there and bust those puppies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:47.21,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.38,0:01:50.21,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't advise it, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:52.79,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Those storm clouds are not like the ones you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:55.72,Luna,,0,0,0,,This far north the weather has a will on it's own.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:57.66,Luna,,0,0,0,,And now it will only grow stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:01:59.34,Luna,,0,0,0,,enveloping everything on ot's path.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:01.69,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Including the Crystal Empire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.69,0:02:03.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And us along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:08.85,Spike,,0,0,0,,There's gotta be something…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:14.84,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I know Princess Twilight is keen on the two of us rekindling our friendship, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:16.28,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,It's been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:19.02,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I don't see how anything on that list is going to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.02,0:02:22.00,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I know, right? It's not like there's some spell
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:25.27,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,that would magically compell us to pick up where we left off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:27.08,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Um, actually there are several.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.28,0:02:32.65,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Mist Mane's material amity, Rock Hoof's rapport, Flash Prance's fellow… ship…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.53,0:02:36.63,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,But I get the feeling the Princess isn't looking for a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:38.64,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Definitely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:39.38,Spike,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:41.05,Spike,,0,0,0,,"And if all else fails,"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:44.43,Spike,,0,0,0,,"ask them to share an embarassing moment from their past,"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:47.26,Spike,,0,0,0,,"Maybe even something they regret."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:50.85,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Uh… I don't see how that would help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:52.54,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:54.53,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,We should just get out of your mane.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.53,0:02:57.83,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,It's pretty obvious this isn't going how Twilight hoped,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:03:01.32,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,and i'm sure you have plenty of important work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:02.38,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:04.20,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Oh! Right. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:07.14,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,No rest for the wizardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:08.76,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Come on, spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:19.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There must be a spell that could restore the Crystal Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:21.12,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:23.26,Celestia,,0,0,0,,But it isn't something that either of us know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:27.61,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,The library here at the castle is nearly as extensive as the one in Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:29.97,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,There's a good chance we can find something there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:31.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Can you hold off the storm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:33.11,Luna,,0,0,0,,Yes, for a time, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:36.77,Luna,,0,0,0,,even our magic will eventually succumb to the power of the Frozen North.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:38.61,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,We will do what we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:40.15,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,But you must hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:56.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't know how long it will take to find the right spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:59.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but you should probably tell the crowd outside to get somewhere warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:02.01,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,And try not to mention the Crystal Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:03.91,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,We don't want to start a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:04.55,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:06.06,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Come on, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:08.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna need all of your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The crystal library is enormous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:12.46,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,You can count on us, Twily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:19.78,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Where'd she go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:28.44,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:32.47,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Well, Spike,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:35.08,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,looks like my biggest fears came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:39.13,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be surprised if Twilight decides to give up on me entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:41.54,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:44.59,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who said all we needed was this list.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:50.94,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,It's not the list, Spike, or you, or Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:53.39,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I'm the one Sunburst doesn't want to be friends with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:56.65,Spike,,0,0,0,,I don't remember him saying he didn't want to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:58.92,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,He didn't have to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:03.48,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, Twilight obviously thinks you're worth being friends with,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:04.79,Spike,,0,0,0,,and I do, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:07.43,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:11.56,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,At least I have two friends, even if one of them has dragon breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:16.13,Spike,,0,0,0,,That's not dragon breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:17.65,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:19.66,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:20.16,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:23.06,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I thought the Crystal Heart was supposed to keep the cold weather out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:24.13,Spike,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:25.26,Spike,,0,0,0,,Unless something's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:25.76,Spike,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:35.19,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We're just saying that it might not be the best idea to stay outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:37.61,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I camped out all night for this spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:39.37,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I'm not about to just give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:46.29,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Still, when you think about it, the view is just as good a little further back, like…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:47.95,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,inside your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:52.78,Somepony,,0,0,0,,The Crystalling Ceremony is one ot our most sacred traditions!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:55.19,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And when that foal is held before the Crystal Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:57.54,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I plan to be as close to the action as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:06:01.63,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I don't know if there's gonna be a Crystalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.10,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,The truth is…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:04.21,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,The baby is an alicorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:06.64,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And her magic's plum crazy, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:09.30,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You might not want to be that close aftrer all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.98,Somepony,,0,0,0,,A baby alicorn? Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:13.65,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:16.49,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Those little wings are probably so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:18.01,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I know. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.01,0:06:22.26,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Look. I am a hundreed percent sure the Crystalling isn't happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:30.32,Somepony,,0,0,0,,No Crystalling, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.63,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Then why are they starting a firework show?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:40.17,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Young filly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:42.36,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:44.84,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Come to your auntie Pinkie Pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:46.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,"Brindle Buck's boat chants"…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:48.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…"Hayhoof's entombments"…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:50.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,"Mystic maps and mazes"…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:52.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Anything up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:54.11,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:56.31,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,I'm not even sure how these are organized.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:06.56,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Shining Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:08.86,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,I thought you were taking care of the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:11.74,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,I'm trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:18.40,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:21.62,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:40.29,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:42.03,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You want the long or the short version?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:42.90,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Short?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.30,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,The baby is an alicorn and she accidentally destroyed the Crystal Heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.65,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,so Twilight and Cadance are looking for a spell to put it back together
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:51.48,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,and save the Crystal Empire from turning into a giant wasteland of ice and snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:07:59.09,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,What about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:01.30,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,"Trotter's Tome of Reliquary"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:04.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I think this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:07.05,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Spell of relic reconstitution.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:08.75,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that we found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:10.11,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:11.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Without this I don't know what we'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:29.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That spell was the only thing we found in the whole library
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:31.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,that was even close to that we needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:34.16,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:36.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:38.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,None of us were expecting any of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:40.84,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can remember the spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:42.57,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I only read it through once!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:47.15,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well, if anypony can exactly remember something that she read for the first time two minutes ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:48.71,Rarity,,0,0,0,,it's you, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:50.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:52.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But I'm not sure how long it will take.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:56.27,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is quickly an option?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:57.97,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,I'll help if I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:00.49,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,But we should evacuate the city just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:04.57,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,You need to lead everypony to the train station before the tracks freeze over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:06.87,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,We will. But between you and Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:08.81,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you remember the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:14.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I only hope this spell is the one we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:19.12,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Is there anything I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:22.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm just sorry about your lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:23.64,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Oh, that doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:26.49,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Sunburst and I don't have anything in common anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:28.68,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,He's a big important wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:31.50,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And I'm relearning everything I ever thought I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:32.66,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Sunburst?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:34.80,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,I don't recognize the name, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.23,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,If he is an important wizard
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:37.78,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,you should bring him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:40.42,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Maybe he'll know what to do if the spell fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:41.26,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:44.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You better go with her, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:58.75,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Sunburst!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:00.44,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Haven't you looked outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:02.71,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:05.32,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,That's not right, the Crystal Heart…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:06.39,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:08.91,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,The baby — Shining Armor and Cadence's baby
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:10.32,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,it's an alicorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:12.50,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:13.29,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:14.77,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And her magic is a little berserk
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:16.52,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,and well, I guess she destroyed the Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:17.75,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,But Twilight thinks she can fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:19.84,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And Princess Cadence thought you could help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:21.92,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:22.84,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:26.75,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You're an important wizard of the Crystal Empire, it just makes sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:27.48,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:29.29,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Right, right-right-right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:33.19,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,You know, I'd like to help, I really would.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:35.17,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I just have so much…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:37.57,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Important wizard work to do around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.85,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You can't stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:44.53,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Did I mention this was a royal Crystalling?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:47.00,Somepony,,0,0,0,,When a crystaller holds the young one aloft,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:50.14,Somepony,,0,0,0,,all of the empire will share their joy and light,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:54.52,Somepony,,0,0,0,,and the Crystal Heart will beat stronger than it ever has before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:56.94,Somepony,,0,0,0,,It really is a moving ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:11:00.80,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I really don't think it's going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.35,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's freezing out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:06.04,Somepony,,0,0,0,,This is the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:08.16,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We've seen snow before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:10.05,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Not like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:12.29,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,We don't have time to argue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:15.66,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadence has decided to evacuate the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:17.95,Somepony,,0,0,0,,But the Crystalling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:21.42,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,I don't know if we'll ever have another Crystalling again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:23.04,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Heart…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:24.07,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Is shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:28.75,Somepony,,0,0,0,,It's not safe here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:32.96,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,That's what we've been trying to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:40.84,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Sunburst, I know you're busy, but did you hear what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:42.04,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Oh, I heard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:45.93,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,But like I said, when you're an important wizard, the work just piles up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:47.36,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Sunburst!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.58,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Look, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:52.48,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I wanna help, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:53.95,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,But I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:55.17,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I wish I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:56.85,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.85,0:11:58.43,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Fixing an ancient relic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:12:01.15,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I can't even come close to doing something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:04.17,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,But I thought you were an important wizard…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:06.72,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Well, you were wrong, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:08.74,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I'm not an important wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:10.64,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I'm not even a wizard at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:22.83,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I know it's hard for you to understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:25.69,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,but not all of us end up achieving greatness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:29.03,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,What? Why wouldn't I understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:30.34,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:32.71,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,You're the protégé of the Princes of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:35.64,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I don't think she picks just anypony for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:38.96,Spike,,0,0,0,,Technically, she's more of a student than a protégé.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:41.65,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:45.18,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I'm not the big important wizard you were expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:48.92,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Sunburst, I don't care if you're a wizard or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:50.34,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I'm just surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:52.56,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You always knew so much about magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:54.53,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I mean, look at all these books.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:56.42,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:58.09,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,reading about magic is one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.68,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,but you don't know what it was like at magic school!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:04.09,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,To know so much and not be able to do any of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:09.45,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't know what it was like to be left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:13.05,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And then getting so bitter that you steal the cutiemarks from the entire village,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:15.00,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,and then get defeated by Twilight and her friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.79,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,so you travel through time to get back at them,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:19.06,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,but they beat you again and teach you about friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:21.82,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,but you're so terrified ponies will find out what you did
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:23.98,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,that you can't make any friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:32.33,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Did you really travel through time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:35.38,Spike,,0,0,0,,See? I told you he'd be impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:37.70,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry we lost touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:40.98,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Maybe if I had reached out you could've helped me at magic school
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:42.48,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,and I could've helped you…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:44.55,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Not become totally evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:48.85,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Lets just say,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:52.71,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I know, what it's like to have something you're not exacly proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:55.77,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,You showed up thinking I'm some big wizard…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:57.03,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:59.10,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I should have told you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:00.31,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:02.20,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,At least we worked it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:04.24,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I think Twilight would be proud of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:06.52,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, if you ever want to tell her about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:08.27,Spike,,0,0,0,,we should probably leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:09.66,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I forgot to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:11.12,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,They're evacuating the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.11,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You need to get to the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:16.03,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Unless you've got a spell here that would drive back the Frozen North
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.03,0:14:19.27,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,and fix the Chystal Heart, so the baby can have a Crystalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:20.63,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Crystalling…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:22.17,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:36.73,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Push them back, my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:47.62,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.43,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Just a little bit further, y'all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:04.95,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,The station is just ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.89,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,We have to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:14.51,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I know how to stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:25.69,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I think that's everything…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:28.71,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,It looks right to me, but
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:30.80,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,there's only one way find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:48.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The spell failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:49.88,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't know what else to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:52.99,Celestia,,0,0,0,,An old student of mine believes he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:59.10,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,The baby did this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:00.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I tried putting it back together with—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.97,0:16:03.82,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,The spell of Relic Reconstitution. No, that won't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:05.83,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Heart's been around for millennia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:09.00,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Restoring a relic like this is way beyond one spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:13.03,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,You need to combine it with something else. Something unique to the relic itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:16.71,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Something that strengthens it and provides it with power…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.41,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The Crystalling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:24.34,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Combining that spell with the light and love of everypony gathered for the ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:25.80,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,together with…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:29.88,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Somnambula's Weather Abjuration to clear away the snow, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:33.01,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,a little Fledgling's Forbearance for the parents… Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:37.91,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,That should curb the little one's power fluctuations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:41.53,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,You must be Sunburst.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.53,0:16:44.06,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Starlight said you were a powerful wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:45.56,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm no wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:50.07,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,He studied magic his whole life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:51.58,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You should see his house!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.77,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And since no pony has any better ideas,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:55.77,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,what do we have to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:02.41,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,I had planned on asking Twilight to be our crystaller,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.95,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,but since it seems like she'll be busy…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.08,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I'd be honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:11.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, what are we waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:57.42,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Citizens! May I present the newest member of the Crystal Empire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:07.28,Somepony,,0,0,0,,She is beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:10.06,Somepony,,0,0,0,,It's just so moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:19:00.21,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Best. Crystaling. Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:05.58,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,For a pony who isn't great at magic
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:07.27,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,you did pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:08.93,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:13.10,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you found a way to share your unique gift, Sunburst.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:15.98,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You may be more of a wizard than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:24.45,NightLight,,0,0,0,,You would not believe the crazy weather that delayed our train.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:25.79,NightLight,,0,0,0,,Came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:29.42,TwilightVelvet,,0,0,0,,But it was all worth it to see this peaceful little angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.42,0:19:31.58,TwilightVelvet,,0,0,0,,Ah, so sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:33.28,TwilightVelvet,,0,0,0,,Come to your grandmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:37.52,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Peaceful now, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:40.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I suppose that spell really did the trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:52.66,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,We have Sunburst to thank for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:55.93,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,I hope he takes his role as crystaller seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:59.14,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Something tells me the baby will need a pony like him
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:01.30,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,to look to for magical advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.68,TwilightVelvet,,0,0,0,,Cadence, darling,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:04.54,TwilightVelvet,,0,0,0,,when are we gonna name the poor little dear,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.54,0:20:07.84,TwilightVelvet,,0,0,0,,or we gonna spend the entire visit just calling her "the baby"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:10.60,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,We were thinking…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:12.06,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Flurry Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:14.27,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,You know, to remember the occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:17.57,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Goodness, how could anypony forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:19.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I think it's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:26.82,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Well, I think you're the Crystal Empire's big important wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:28.45,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Whether you like it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.78,0:20:31.04,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'll have time for any wizarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:33.75,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I'm a crystaller now, that's a big responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:36.78,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I can't think of anypony more qualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:38.79,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Just promise you'll stay in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:42.32,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Like I'd ever lose touch with my oldest friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:48.52,Spike,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:50.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:53.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I think I have a lot to learn about being a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:55.23,Spike,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.62,Spike,,0,0,0,,Your lesson went perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.62,0:20:59.69,Spike,,0,0,0,,Starlight and Sunburst got over their past to rekindle their friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:01.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No thanks to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.10,0:21:02.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I know, a lot happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.63,0:21:06.57,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I just wish I could have given my pupil the attention she deserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:11.44,Spike,,0,0,0,,I know she needed to be put on the right path.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:14.71,Spike,,0,0,0,,Giving her the space to make her own decisions worked pretty well,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:17.16,Spike,,0,0,0,,isn't that how Celestia taught you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:20.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You know, I never thought about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:21.55,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but I guess it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:24.52,Spike,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're a better teacher than you thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:37.10,Auto,,0,0,0,,СЧАСТЛИВЫЙ ПОНЕЦ
